#: ../../talk/call_views.rst:3
msgid "Call layout"
msgstr "Leagan amach glaonna"

#: ../../talk/call_views.rst:5
msgid ""
"You can switch between promoted view and grid view using the toggle in the "
"bottom bar."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat aistriú idir an radharc chun cinn agus an radharc greille trí"
" úsáid a bhaint as an lasc sa bharra bun."

#: ../../talk/call_views.rst:11
msgid "Grid view"
msgstr "Radharc eangaí"

#: ../../talk/call_views.rst:13
msgid ""
"Grid view shows as many participants as the screen can fit. Use the "
"navigation buttons on the left and right to scroll through participants when"
" there are more than the screen can display."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann an radharc eangaí an oiread rannpháirtithe agus is féidir a "
"fheistiú ar an scáileán. Úsáid na cnaipí nascleanúna ar chlé agus ar dheis "
"chun scrollú trí na rannpháirtithe nuair a bhíonn níos mó ann ná mar is "
"féidir leis an scáileán a thaispeáint."

#: ../../talk/call_views.rst:19
msgid "Promoted view"
msgstr "Radharc curtha chun cinn"

#: ../../talk/call_views.rst:21
msgid ""
"Promoted view shows the active speaker large, with other participants in a "
"row below. Use the navigation buttons on the left and right to scroll "
"through participants when the row overflows."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann an radharc ardaithe an cainteoir gníomhach i bhformáid mhór, "
"agus rannpháirtithe eile i sraith thíos. Úsáid na cnaipí nascleanúna ar chlé"
" agus ar dheis chun scrollú trí na rannpháirtithe nuair a bhíonn an tsraith "
"ró-líonta."
